About This Blog

The Sacramento Bee's team of health reporters covers California health care, medicine and healthy living, with an emphasis on public health and under-served communities.Sammy Caiola: Health care and healthy living. Reach her at scaiola@sacbee.com or 916-321-1636. Twitter: @SammyCaiola Claudia Buck: Public health and consumer issues. Reach her at cbuck@sacbee.com or 916-321-1968.
